823
00:43:28,620 --> 00:43:29,780
with cola and Perrier water.

824
00:43:30,020 --> 00:43:30,460
OK.

825
00:43:31,380 --> 00:43:32,260
Have it ready by next Friday.

826
00:43:32,940 --> 00:43:34,940
Didn't you say he'd be here on Monday?

827
00:43:38,300 --> 00:43:39,740
I don't think he'll arrive so soon.

828
00:43:41,900 --> 00:43:45,780
He has some private business
that is un...finished.

829
00:43:46,260 --> 00:43:48,180
Oh, we're finished. Thanks, everyone.

830
00:43:57,300 --> 00:43:59,380
So, we're not finished. Sorry, I heard wrong.

831
00:44:00,700 --> 00:44:01,380
That'll be all.

832
00:44:04,220 --> 00:44:05,100
Xing Yun, stay behind.

833
00:44:11,680 --> 00:44:12,620
You didn't sleep well yesterday.

834
00:44:13,780 --> 00:44:14,380
Kind of.

835
00:44:15,660 --> 00:44:17,220
It seems working 12/7

836
00:44:17,220 --> 00:44:17,780
is a better fit for you.

837
00:44:18,820 --> 00:44:19,740
I guess so.

838
00:44:20,180 --> 00:44:22,580
They say home is where the heart is.

839
00:44:22,580 --> 00:44:23,980
I feel like the office is my home.

840
00:44:23,980 --> 00:44:25,260
I won't leave early again.

841
00:44:28,860 --> 00:44:29,940
Sorry, Mr. Xia.

842
00:44:29,940 --> 00:44:31,860
I shouldn't have slept through the meeting.

843
00:44:32,100 --> 00:44:33,900
Your voice is so hypnotic.

844
00:44:33,900 --> 00:44:35,140
Get some sleep on the sofa.

845
00:44:40,540 --> 00:44:42,740
Is this sarcasm?

846
00:44:43,180 --> 00:44:44,380
Are you testing me?

847
00:44:45,420 --> 00:44:47,420
Seeing your sleepless face
makes me uncomfortable.

848
00:44:50,380 --> 00:44:51,580
Then, I'm very sorry.

849
00:44:52,500 --> 00:44:53,340
Are you going to sleep or not?

850
00:44:53,860 --> 00:44:55,420
I am, I am.

851
00:45:03,500 --> 00:45:04,540
It smells comfortable.

852
00:45:05,140 --> 00:45:06,580
It looks like you slack off often.
